{"tid":219144,"cid":28,"subCid":0,"title":"新分唇 Spoiler Tag","createTime":"2017-04-27T04:25:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T07:13:30.000Z","uid":28759,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd55518d6f4965f96a8bbcdcf131236d953cf984","tid":219144,"uid":28759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T04:25:32.000Z","msg":"既然都有 upvote 同 downvote<br />\n咁 spoiler 都係一個相當重要嘅 tag<br />\n<br />\n例子 1<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>上錯婆婆 online 集中討論區<br />\n簡介<br />\n[spoiler]玩得多會上癮 blah blah blah blah... 玩得耐返唔到轉頭[/spoiler]<br />\n<br />\nQ&amp;A<br />\n[spoiler]1. 有冇得鋤學生妹？<br />\n冇<br />\n<br />\n2. 有冇得鋤伯伯<br />\n有[/spoiler]</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n例子 2<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>House of Thrones 集中討論區<br />\n今集 Skye 真係好撚正 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n[spolier]佢同張智霖果場打戲睇到我濕晒[/spoiler]</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n例子 3<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>仆街夏惠姨真係好淫底<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過我鍾意 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </blockquote><br />\n咁用 spoiler tag 包住後面果句，就唔駛隔咁撚多行"},{"pid":"f17025e5fa226a865221bc6ff83af7d32ab9e074","tid":219144,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:00:59.000Z","msg":"正經野冇人理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e05d4c2adb8d2f387076881af1e7c179607688","tid":219144,"uid":25846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T01:10:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正經野冇人理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連登d中小學雞spoiler 呢隻字都唔識啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw 支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e6117a42385b7932d9243cec90b5044a0a4dd0","tid":219144,"uid":2151